  "body": "In mainnet config, `SafetyDecay` is defined is `1/10` which is 0 for uint64. The spec uses 10% for float which we would love to avoid at all cost. Working with Aditya on this\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/master/shared/params/mainnet_config.go#L135\r\n\r\nThanks @prestonvanloon for pointing this out",
